      <title>欧洲游客开始避免我们成为“未知领土”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/european-tourists-start-avoiding-the-us-as-unknown-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国酒店集团Accor SA警告说，今年夏天从欧洲到美国的远期预订下降了25％，因为那些被总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的边境钳位转移到其他地点的旅行者推迟了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/european-tourists-start-avoiding-the-us-as-unknown-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 09:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
